short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Loads a TeraScore on every Roblox profile

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension displays a unique TeraScore on every Roblox profile. TeraScores are a fun way to rank profiles on Roblox, it takes in account several factors which can be used to gauge how 'good' a profile is!
